    "body": "## ✅ PR Ready for Review\n\nThe snapshot implementation is complete and ready for review. Here's what has been verified:\n\n### Implementation Summary\n- **7 files changed**: 5 new helper scripts, 1 setup script, updated README.md and install.sh\n- **All scripts validated**: Syntax checked with `bash -n` - all passed ✅\n- **No CI failures**: Repository has no CI configured, no issues to address\n- **Branch up to date**: Master branch is merged and current\n- **No uncommitted changes**: All work is committed and pushed\n\n### Features Implemented\n✅ Automatic snapshots on package updates (snap-pac)\n✅ Hourly timeline snapshots with configurable retention\n✅ Bootable snapshots via GRUB menu (grub-btrfs)\n✅ 5 helper commands: create, list, diff, delete, rollback\n✅ Graceful handling of non-Btrfs filesystems\n✅ Complete documentation in README\n\n### Files Added/Modified\n- `scripts/snapshot_setup.sh` - Main setup script (410 lines)\n- `bin/snapshot-create` - Create manual snapshots\n- `bin/snapshot-list` - List all snapshots\n- `bin/snapshot-diff` - Compare snapshots\n- `bin/snapshot-delete` - Delete snapshots\n- `bin/snapshot-rollback` - Show rollback instructions\n- `install.sh` - Integration with main installer\n- `README.md` - Documentation for snapshot features\n\nAll requirements from issue #8 have been fulfilled. The implementation improves system stability through snapshot support as requested.\n\n**PR URL**: https://github.com/eg0rmaffin/vapor-rice-i3/pull/13",
